                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>ers as owe you I will endeavor<lb/> to collect same, as I know you are<lb/> too\n                lenient &amp; perhaps careless in such<lb/> matters.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Your friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                <add>?</add>\n                <persName role=\"author\">M Arnold</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
